## Amendment of the European Parliament

(43) ‘national competent authority’ means any of the national authorities which are responsible for the enforcement of this Regulation;

‘national competent authority’ means the national supervisory authority, the notifying authority and the market surveillance authority ;

‘national competent authority’ means any of the national authorities which are responsible for the enforcement of this Regulation;

